title: James Taylor - Live 1993 [2 Disc] MP3 @ 320
description:
The Essential Taylor

James Taylor - Live MP3 @ 320kbps

Live is singer-songwriter James Taylor's fifteenth album, and first live album. Released in 1993, this double CD presents selections from 14 shows during a November 1992 tour. Live peaked at number 20 on Billboard magazine's Billboard 200.[2]
